        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Anyone can follow a recipe. But not everyone can cook.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "That’s because the difference between a novice cook and a pro isn’t knowing how to follow a recipe.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "And designers of all kinds have a",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "process",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ", too. A system of steps that guides their thinking and their choices.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://www.interaction-design.org/literature/article/5-stages-in-the-design-thinking-process"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "What differentiates a poor design from a great one isn’t how precise the designer followed each step, but what they did in between.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It’s actually pretty easy to learn the process. Just look it up.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "But the stuff in the gaps—the seeing, discerning, ideating, making, facilitating and communicating,",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "the real skills of the trade",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "—that takes a lifetime to master.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}